lyrics:
[Verse]
You're the love of my life, the one I adore
With each cheesy bite, I always crave for more
You're saucy and bold, a taste I can't resist
You make my heart skip a beat, with every pizza kiss

[Chorus]
Pizza, oh pizza, you make my taste buds dance
You bring joy and happiness, with every single chance
Pizza, my love, we're a perfect match
Forever together, like cheese and tomato, attached
